link_desc:
Basic Monitoring of SEH MyUTN-80 DongleServer. Probably works with other MyUTN devices of SEH. too.

  • Serial Number
  • Firmware Version
  • AutoDiscovery of USB-Ports

Macros for AutoDiscovery:

  • {$PORT.TAG.MATCHES}
    • Assigned Tag of USB Port
  • {$PORT.TAG.NOT_MATCHES}
  • {$PORT.SERIAL.MATCHES}
    • Serial of connected USB-Device
  • {$PORT.SERIAL.NOT_MATCHES}
  • {$PORT.SLOT.MATCHES}
    • Slot of USB Port
  • {$PORT.SLOT.NOT_MATCHES}

Trigger:

  • Connection Status of {#PORTSLOT} ({#PORTTAG}) Changed
author: Sascha Plumhoff
